                            <p class="text-muted small"><span class="fw-semibold text-dark">Technologies:</span> Visual Basic, Windows Forms, UI</p>
                        </div>
                        <button class="btn btn-outline-secondary w-100 mt-4 rounded-pill">View Details</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Project 3: Parking Slot System - subtle yellow/gold hue -->
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm rounded-4 overflow-hidden bg-warning-subtle">
                    <div style="height: 200px; overflow: hidden;">
                        <img src="~/Image/Parking.png" class="w-100 h-100" style="object-fit: cover;" alt="Parking Slot System screenshot" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column justify-content-between p-4">
                        <div>
                            <h5 class="card-title fw-bold text-warning-emphasis mb-3">Parking Slot System</h5>
                            <p class="card-text text-secondary small mb-4">A Python-based desktop application utilizing CustomTkinter to automate real-time slot tracking, floor management, entry/exit timestamp logs, and error-free payment calculations.</p>
                            <p class="text-muted small"><span class="fw-semibold text-dark">Technologies:</span> Python, CustomTkinter, Database, OOP</p>
                        </div>
                        <button class="btn btn-outline-warning w-100 mt-4 rounded-pill">View Details</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
